title: Drunk Tech Review (Mischa Pollock)
description: This week we're joined by Mischa Pollock of Drunk Tech Review.  Mischa has a new show on National Geographic; Machine Impossible where he travels the world sampling all manner of strange machinery including, boats w/ tank tracks, jet packs and high speed manned air foils.
author: matt@thesmokingtire.com (Matt Farah & Zack Klapman)
